      </ul>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>
          Enter the sixteen digit account number on your CopperLine Card:
          <div class="tooltip-item">
            ?
            <div class="tooltip tooltip-image">
              <img src="images/cc.png">
              <p>Your account number is the number on the front of your Copperline Account Card. If you don’t have your card, call 800-260-4897 ext 2 and activate your account through a call center agent.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h3>
        <div class="inputs">
          <input type="tel" name="" placeholder="1111–1111–1111–1111">
        </div>
          <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button add-break" value="Next" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>You’re from ABC Technology Company, LLC, is that correct? </h3>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button grey-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>Is Michael Jones still the President of ABC Technology company?</h3>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button grey-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>Are you Michael Jones?</h3>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button grey-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>Michael, enter your e-mail address and your phone number: </h3>
        <div class="inputs">
          <input type="email" placeholder="name@example.com" />
          <input type="tel" placeholder="(111)-111-1111" />
        </div>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Next" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>
          Michael, are you the 100% owner of ABC Technology?
          <div class="tooltip-item">
            ?
            <div class="tooltip">
              <p>We need to verify and understand the ownership structure of your company.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h3>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button grey-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>
          Michael, for your protection, we need to verify your identity through Experian. Is this acceptable?
          <div class="tooltip-item">
            ?
            <div class="tooltip">
              <p>We use the Experian credit report to verify your identity and to provide you with a pre-qualification for credit for your company. This is a “soft pull” of your report for pre-screening purposes. It will not affect your credit score or put an inquiry on your report. We will reserve the right to pull your credit report if you choose to accept the terms and conditions of our loan offer.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h3>
        <p>This will not affect your FICO credit score and there will be no inquiry on your credit report.  View <a href="#" target="_blank">terms and conditions</a>.</p>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button grey-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>
          Michael, enter your home address and date of birth so we can verify this information with the Experian credit report.
          <div class="tooltip-item">
            ?
            <div class="tooltip">
              <p>We use the  your home address to match with your Experian credit report. This is a “soft pull” of your report for pre-screening purposes. It will not affect your credit score or put an inquiry on your report. </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h3>
        <label>Home Address</label>
        <div class="inputs full-input">
          <input type="text" placeholder="Street" />
        </div>
        <div class="inputs third-input">
          <input type="text" placeholder="City" />
          <input type="text" placeholder="State" />
          <input type="number" placeholder="Zip Code" />
        </div>
        <label>Date of Birth</label>
        <div class="inputs half-input">
          <input type="text" placeholder="MM/DD/YYYY" />
        </div>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Next" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset>
        <h3>Your company was founded in 2006, is that correct?</h3>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button grey-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>And you have 7 employees, is that correct?</h3>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button grey-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>Your annual revenues are about $310,000 is that correct?</h3>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button grey-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>
          What was your approximate profit last year?
          <div class="tooltip-item">
            ?
            <div class="tooltip">
              <p>Loans do not require profitability but it may affect the rates and terms of your loan offer.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h3>
        <input class="slider" value="0" min="-75000" max="75000" name="rangeslider" type="range" />
        <ul class="three-range">
          <li>- $75,500</li>
          <li>$0</li>
          <li>$75,500</li>
        </ul>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Next" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>
          What does your company need the money for? <span>(Check all that apply.)</span>
          <div class="tooltip-item">
            ?
            <div class="tooltip">
              <p>Use of funds my affect the rates and terms. For example, we typically extend longer terms and give better rates if you are acquiring equipment because the equipment becomes collateral for the loan. </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h3>
        <div class="radio-buttons two-column-checkboxes" action="">
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="checkbox" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Expansion</label>
          </label>
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="checkbox" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Equipment</label>
          </label>
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="checkbox" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Inventory</label>
          </label>
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="checkbox" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Other stuff</label>
          </label>
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="checkbox" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Cash Flow</label>
          </label>
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="checkbox" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Remodel</label>
          </label>
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="checkbox" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Pay Vendors</label>
          </label>
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="checkbox" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Vehicles</label>
          </label>
        </div>
        <br><br>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h3>
          Congratulations Michael, we have successfully verified your identity and are ready to discuss loan options with you. If the terms are right, how quickly do you want the funds?
          <div class="tooltip-item">
            ?
            <div class="tooltip">
              <p>If you need the funds right away we can connect you with an account manager who can help you through the process, help you to choose the right loan for you and answer any questions. </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h3>
        <div class="radio-buttons next" action="">
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="radio" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Immediately</label>
          </label>
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="radio" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Next Month</label>
          </label>
          <label class="radio">
            <input type="radio" name="test" value="test">
            <span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>
            <label>Not sure</label>
          </label>
        </div>
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset>
        <h5>You're All Set!</h5>
        <h3>Your CopperLine Account Manager is going to be Sharon Boyer. Here’s Sharon’s contact information.</h3>
        <div class="contact-block">
          <img src="images/sharon.jpg" class="point-of-contact">
          <div class="contact-info">
            <p><strong>Sharon Boyer</strong> <br>800-260-4897 x713<br>sharon@copperlineusa.com</p>
            <p>Branch Office: Chicago</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr><br>
        <p>She’s going to give you some different financing options and verify your revenue prior to funding.</p>
      </fieldset>
    </form>
  </section>

